# HealthSentinel Root Gitignore

# --- Wildcard Matches (Recursive) ---
**/node_modules/
**/__pycache__/
**/venv/
**/.venv/
**/env/
**/.next/
**/.pytest_cache/

# --- Environment & Secrets ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Build Outputs ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/

# --- OS & IDE ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.log

# --- Docker ---
.docker/

# --- Infrastructure & Deployment Scripts ---
# Ignore local infrastructure configurations (JSON files with ARNs)
infrastructure/**/*.json

# Ignore temporary CLI policy files
secrets-policy.json

# --- Terraform ---
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
override.tf
override.tf.json
cluster_addons

# --- Infrastructure Scripts (Keep scripts, ignore configs) ---
healthsentinel-frontend/infrastructure/ecs/*.json
